{
  "text": "Here we propose to evaluate the visible quantities E and P at the RECO level, i.e. in terms of the reconstructed objects, namely jets, muons, electrons and photons [CITATION_1] . To be precise, let there be N obj reconstructed objects in the event, with energies E i and 3-momenta P i , i = 1, 2, . . . , N obj , correspondingly. Then in place of (2.6-2.8), let us instead identify",
